The '''Arad Power Station''' is a large [[thermal power plant]] located in [[Arad, Romania|Arad]], having 2 generation groups of 50 [[Watt#Megawatt|MW]] each  and one generating unit of 12 MW having a total [[electricity]] generation capacity of 112 MW.<ref>[http://www.cet.arad.ro/capacitati.htm Capacitati CET Arad {{ro}}] {{webarchive |url=https://web.archive.org/web/20081013202418/http://www.cet.arad.ro/capacitati.htm |date=October 13, 2008 }}</ref>

The eastern chimney of the power station's two chimneys is 201 meters tall.

