The '''Gheorgheni Wind Farm''' is a proposed wind power project in [[Gheorgheni]], [[Harghita County]], [[Romania]]. It will have 38 individual [[wind turbine]]s<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.zf.ro/companii/energie/o-firma-cu-actionariat-ungar-vrea-sa-construiasca-in-harghita-un-parc-eolian-de-100-mw-7752360|title=O firmă cu acţionariat ungar vrea să construiască în Harghita un parc eolian de 100 MW|publisher=''Ziarul Financiar''|language=Romanian|accessdate=2010-11-26}}</ref> with a nominal output of around 2.6 [[Watt#Megawatt|MW]] each which will deliver up to 100 MW of power, enough to power over 60,000 homes, with a capital investment required of approximately US$150 million.

