'''Save Our Selves''' is the name of a group of [[activists]] organized to raise [[awareness]] of [[global climate change]]. They are the organizers of the July 2007 [[Live Earth]] concerts.
The group was founded by [[Kevin Wall]], and includes as major partners former [[United States]] [[Vice President of the United States|Vice President]] [[Al Gore]], the [[Alliance for Climate Protection]], [[MSN]] and [[Control Room (film)|Control Room]], a concert production company producing Live Earth.{{Citation needed|date=April 2010}}
